Package: DivABC
Title: An ABC approach to estimate parameters in DAISIE/TRAISIE and SSE models.
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2025-12-25
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Shu",
           family = "Xie",
           role = c("aut","cre"),
           email = "s.xie@rug.nl"))
Description: Using an ABC-SMC algorithm to estimate diversification rates  
    of simulated phylogenies from DAISIE and state-dependent diversification 
    models (BiSSE/MuSSE/GeoSSE/TraiSIE).We compare the estimated rates with 
    which from likelihood-based methods (MLE and MCMC). 
